/**
 * Callback for initializing service. Displayed as a global member.
 * @callback jibo.gl~Callback
 * @param {String} error `null` if no error.
 * @param {Object} result Data structure using the following format:
 * ```
 * {
 *    Input: "hello my name is Joe I work in a button factory"
 *    NLParse: {
 *       who: "Joe",
 *       what: "Button factory"
 *    }
 * }
 * ```
 */

/**
 * @description
 * Global Listener for Holistic Dialogue Management.
 * In addition to one-off listening, there will exist listen behaviors which
 * self-enroll in the Global Listening process. They will send a request to the
 * GLService, which will manage the messages they receive.
 * Listen requests will be communicated through a web socket, opened by a server
 * manged by the GLService.
 *
 * ```
 * var gl = require("jibo").gl;
 * ```
 * @property events {jibo.gl.StateEvents} Typed events of gl module.
 * @property global {jibo.gl.GlobalEvents} Typed global events of gl module.
 * @namespace jibo.gl
 */

